These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, rock, electronic
1. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking juice is the fan of electronic##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee | juice   |
| Music-Genre      | folk    | rock  | electronic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, blood-red, purple
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, nigerian
1. the argentine is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the canadian is the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Color      | blood-red | green     | purple      |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, marigold, iris
There 3 different types of food: plum, radish, raspberry
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Flower   | dahlia | iris  | marigold       |
| Food       | plum     | radish | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, radish, zucchini
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, dubstep, metal
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of metal is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | zucchini    | radish     | pomegranate |
| Music-Genre   | metal | salsa | dubstep     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, hedgehog
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, manager, photographer
1. the manager is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the manager is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the doctor##1
4. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | bird     | hedgehog |
| Job   | photographer        | doctor | manager    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, plum, strawberry
House: cottage, gothic-revival, futuristic
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the cottage house##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the person eating strawberry is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | strawberry | kiwi      | plum  |
| House   | cottage       | gothic-revival | futuristic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, volleyball, baseball
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Sport   | baseball      | climbing     | volleyball    |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goldfish | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris, daffodil
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, card-games, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who growsiris is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Flower    | daffodil | zinnia | iris      |
| Hobby   | camping     | skydiving | card-games |

