.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, police-officer, librarian
3 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the horse is the police-officer##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Job   | librarian | police-officer | firefighter  |
| Pet     | rat     | horse      | rabbit |

