.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, tea
City: colone, edinburgh, prague
1. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | cola   | sprite    | tea    |
| City   | edinburgh | colone | prague |

