.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, soccer
1. the fan of trance is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | trance   | punk  |
| Sport   | soccer    | cricket | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-12::.
