There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, egyptian, nigerian
1. the person watching western movies is in the middle##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure    | western     | documentary   |
| Nationality   | egyptian | brazilian | nigerian |

