.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, yellow, ivory
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, pop
1. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Color      | chestnut  | ivory | yellow  |
| Music-Genre   | funk | pop   | classical |

